In [134]:
def norm_plot(model, grid):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 5))
    plt.title('Непрерывная норма градиента ({})'.format(grid))
    plt.xlabel('время')
    plt.yscale('log')
    plt.plot(model.ts, model.df_additional.iloc[:, 0])
    plt.show()

In [158]:
def derivative_0(model):
    df = model.df_phi.iloc[-1, 1] - model.df_phi.iloc[-1, 0]
    dx = model.xs[1] - model.xs[0]
    return df / dx
for model in [model_cyl_400, model_cyl_800, model_cyl_1600, model_cyl_400_log, model_cyl_800_log,
              model_cyl_1600_log, model_cyl_3200_log]:
    print(derivative_0(model))
